                <h2>What is KJPL (2nd Edition)?</h2>
                <p>KJPL evolves into a military-grade language, blending biblical metaphors with hardened systems programming. Developed by xAI, it’s built for security, real-time performance, and reliability—ready for drones, cryptography, and command systems.</p>
                <p class="quote"><strong>Isaiah 54:17</strong> - <em>“No weapon formed against thee shall prosper.” KJPL stands unassailable.</em></p>

                <h2>Purpose of This Textbook</h2>
                <p>Master KJPL to build systems that endure under fire—literal or digital.</p>
                <p class="quote"><strong>Proverbs 21:31</strong> - <em>“The horse is prepared against the day of battle.”</em></p>

                <h2>Who Should Read This?</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Beginners seeking a robust foundation</li>
                    <li>Developers transitioning to secure systems</li>
                    <li>Military engineers (avionics, C4ISR)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="quote"><strong>Joshua 1:9</strong> - <em>“Be strong and of a good courage.”</em></p>

