                <h2>Syntax & Structure</h2>
                <code>DECLARE FAITH AS STRING = "Mustard_Seed"<br>IF FAITH >= "Mustard_Seed" THEN SECURE_CALL MOVE_MOUNTAINS()</code>
                <p class="quote"><strong>Deuteronomy 32:4</strong> - <em>“A God of truth.”</em></p>

                <h2>Data Types & Collections</h2>
                <code>PROMISES: SECURE_COVENANT = {"Peace": "Shalom"} |> SEAL</code>
                <p class="quote"><strong>Revelation 3:7</strong> - <em>“Key of David.”</em></p>

                <h2>Control Structures</h2>
                <code>FOR DAY: U8 FROM 1 TO 7 DO CREATE("Light", DAY) |> REALTIME ENDFOR</code>
                <p class="quote"><strong>Psalm 119:160</strong> - <em>“Thy word is true.”</em></p>
            </div>
        </details>
